quran[15]{c,v,t}:
  28,61,"Day win iwumi Nefka lemâahda igerzen, u immuger ip, am win i Nezha s l$it n tmeddurt n ddunit; sinna, ass n tnekra, neppa seg wid ara d irsen"
  28,62,"Ass ideg ara sen d Isiwel, ad Yini: \"anda ten wid iyY tepcarakem, u tellam tepkabarem"
  28,63,"A d inin wid i$ef iûaô wawal: \"a Mass nne$! Wigi i njeggeê, njeggeê iten, akken i nepwajeggeê. A nzekki $ureK: maççi d nekwni ay âabden"
  28,64,"Ad asen inin: \"naâôet wid tepcarakem\". Ad ten naâôen, ur asen d pparan. Walan aâaqeb. A lemmer llan pwanhan"
  28,65,"Ass ideg ara sen d Isiwel, ad Yini: \"acu d terram i imazanen"
  28,66,"Assen, ad dergen fellasen isalen, nitni ur pmesteqsayen"
  28,67,"Ma d win isteôoâen, iumnen, ixedmen ayen ilhan, ahat ad yili seg imerbaê"
  28,68,"Mass ik Ixelleq ayen i S ihwan, u Ismenyafa. Ur ten id iûaê usmenyif. Gedha s Öebbi! I Aâlay sennig wayen pcaraken"
  28,69,"Mass ik Iéôa ayen iffren deg idmaren nnsen, akked wayen cennâen"
  28,70,"Neppa d Öebbi, ur illi ôebbi siwa Neppa. I Neppa, annuz di tmezwarut, u di tneggarut. I Neppa aêuddu, $uôeS tu$alin nnwen"
  28,71,"Ini: \"acu tmeyyzem, ma Isse$li d Öebbi iv imezgi, fellawen, alamma d ass n tnekra? Anwa ôebbi, war Öebbi, ara wen d iawin tafat? Day ur tsellem ara"
  28,72,"Ini: \"acu tmeyyzem, ma Issuli Öebbi ass imezgi, fellawen, alamma d ass n tnekra? Anwa ôebbi, war Öebbi, ara wen d iawin iv, a ppestaâfum degs? Day ur tepwalim ara"
  28,73,"Seg uêunu S, Iga yawen iv akked wass, i ustaâfu nnwen, akked unadi n lfevl iS. Amar a ppesnemmrem"
  28,74,"Ass ideg ara sen d Isiwel, ad asen Yini: \"anda ten wid iyY tepcarakem, u tellam tepkabarem"
  28,75,"A d Nawi anagi, si yal lois. A Nini: \"awit ed atebbet nnwen\". Ad éôen ar tidep n Öebbi. Itelf iten wayen d snulfuyen"